<doc id="506377" wikidata="Q2285712" url="?curid=506377" title="Mitry–Claye station">
<text>Mitry–Claye station is a railway station near Paris, France. It is in the commune of Mitry-Mory, and also serves nearby Claye-Souilly. It is served by regional Transilien trains and the Paris RER trains, so is an important transit point.

== See also ==
* List of stations of the Paris RER

